  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. Substituting <em>x</em> = -1 gives <em>q</em>(-1) = 48&middot;2<sup>-1</sup> = 48&middot;(1/2) = 24. Substituting <em>x</em> = 0 gives <em>q</em>(0) = 48&middot;2<sup>0</sup> = 48. Substituting <em>x</em> = 1 gives <em>q</em>(1) = 48&middot;2 = 96. These match the table in choice C. The other choices have at least one incorrect value.</p>",
